name: AFB101
description:
Hand wrapped with African wax fabric from West Africa - Ghana.

Made with vibrant colors and sealed for long lasting wear.
This bangle is great for stacking and adding flair to any outfit! It's perfect for gifts and is guaranteed to make a statement.

Price is for a SINGLE bangle in the photographed fabric; hence no two bangles are identical.
